00:01:31,991 --> 00:01:35,955
<i>[Episode 15]</i>

3
00:01:46,132 --> 00:01:48,692
Unexpectedly, you're a devout believer,
Lady Jing,

4
00:01:50,052 --> 00:01:51,532
Liuli, please stop teasing me,

5
00:01:51,532 --> 00:01:52,732
Although I'm going to worship Buddha,

6
00:01:52,732 --> 00:01:54,412
my heart of self-interest
exceeds worshipping Buddha,

7
00:01:54,932 --> 00:01:56,812
It seems even the Buddha has seen through this,

8
00:01:56,812 --> 00:01:59,572
That's why, despite many years of worship,
my wishes have never been fulfilled,

9
00:02:01,652 --> 00:02:03,332
Lately, I have moved on,

10
00:02:03,892 --> 00:02:05,372
So, I don't have too high expectations,

11
00:02:05,972 --> 00:02:07,532
I wonder what are you praying for,

12
00:02:07,532 --> 00:02:09,252
Is it convenient to tell me?

13
00:02:09,252 --> 00:02:10,492
Actually, it's nothing,

14
00:02:11,092 --> 00:02:12,912
This matter is already known to all,

15
00:02:12,912 --> 00:02:14,452
All this while, those busybodies have

16
00:02:14,452 --> 00:02:16,192
never been short of talking about me
behind my back,

17
00:02:16,192 --> 00:02:17,612
What?

18
00:02:17,612 --> 00:02:18,852
I'm getting more and more curious,

19
00:02:20,812 --> 00:02:22,532
I have been married to Wang Junmeng
for many years,

20
00:02:22,532 --> 00:02:24,152
Liuli, you know this as well,

21
00:02:24,152 --> 00:02:27,412
But I have never borne him a son or a daughter,

22
00:02:28,292 --> 00:02:29,852
At first, I didn't take it seriously,

23
00:02:30,372 --> 00:02:31,712
But as time went on,

24
00:02:31,712 --> 00:02:33,212
it became my heartache,

25
00:02:36,612 --> 00:02:38,692
Of the three unfilial acts,
having no descendants is the worst,

26
00:02:39,612 --> 00:02:41,052
This matter is indeed no small issue,

27
00:02:42,972 --> 00:02:45,292
His elders have actually been
expressing their disapproval for some time,

28
00:02:45,812 --> 00:02:47,492
They also thought about
finding him a concubine,

29
00:02:48,372 --> 00:02:50,052
Besides, I feel guilty about this,

30
00:02:50,572 --> 00:02:51,932
If he really wants a concubine,

31
00:02:52,452 --> 00:02:53,492
I'll stop him,

32
00:02:56,492 --> 00:03:00,252
But he decisively refused all matters
relating to finding a bride,

33
00:03:01,052 --> 00:03:02,892
He would rather have people mock him
behind his back for having no descendants

34
00:03:04,132 --> 00:03:05,252
than let me down,

35
00:03:07,132 --> 00:03:09,772
I didn't expect
Wang Junmeng to be such a devoted person!

36
00:03:10,332 --> 00:03:12,172
It made me see him in a new light,

37
00:03:12,172 --> 00:03:14,972
But the more he does so,
the more guilty I feel,

38
00:03:15,932 --> 00:03:17,012
Over the years,

39
00:03:17,012 --> 00:03:18,752
I have tried all the methods I could,

40
00:03:18,752 --> 00:03:20,172
but none have been effective,

41
00:03:21,052 --> 00:03:24,372
Therefore, the bronze Buddha worshipped
in this Great Buddha Temple

42
00:03:24,372 --> 00:03:26,712
is my wife's only hope,

43
00:03:26,712 --> 00:03:28,692
Is this Great Buddha Temple truly
so miraculous?

44
00:03:29,212 --> 00:03:31,132
Madam Kudi, you have not been in Xizhou
for a long time,

45
00:03:31,132 --> 00:03:32,272
and don't know certain things,

46
00:03:32,272 --> 00:03:34,932
The bronze Buddha in Great Buddha Temple
is extraordinarily miraculous,

47
00:03:34,932 --> 00:03:36,652
Every few years,
it would become real to people,

48
00:03:37,292 --> 00:03:39,972
Back when that cruel
Protector-General Qiao was in office,

49
00:03:39,972 --> 00:03:42,252
he forced people to dig city walls
in the scorching heat,

50
00:03:42,252 --> 00:03:43,572
Many people died,

51
00:03:43,572 --> 00:03:46,672
Within days, the bronze Buddha began
to weep and sweat,

52
00:03:46,672 --> 00:03:48,452
which shook the entire Western Regions,

53
00:03:48,452 --> 00:03:49,992
Protector-General Qiao was also frightened,

54
00:03:49,992 --> 00:03:51,332
So he stopped the forced labor,

55
00:03:51,332 --> 00:03:53,432
Later on, the newly appointed
Protector-General Chai

56
00:03:53,432 --> 00:03:55,412
claimed to promote Taoism over Buddhism,

57
00:03:55,412 --> 00:03:57,792
He intended to build a Taoist temple
in the eastern district,

58
00:03:57,792 --> 00:03:58,972
But within a couple of days,

59
00:03:58,972 --> 00:04:01,112
