just as it had in the past,

60
00:04:01,112 --> 00:04:03,092
The matter of repairing the Taoist temple

61
00:04:03,092 --> 00:04:04,372
was thus left unresolved,

62
00:04:04,892 --> 00:04:07,372
It's truly unheard of

63
00:04:08,132 --> 00:04:09,972
for a bronze Buddha to weep and sweat,

64
00:04:09,972 --> 00:04:11,412
This is not something I made up,

65
00:04:11,412 --> 00:04:13,252
Everyone in Xizhou knows about this,

66
00:04:14,212 --> 00:04:15,452
If it's true,

67
00:04:15,452 --> 00:04:17,012
indeed, it's worth worshipping Buddha,

68
00:04:18,812 --> 00:04:21,652
This time, I will also pray to
the bronze Buddha for you,

69
00:04:21,652 --> 00:04:23,732
Perhaps the two of us together

70
00:04:23,732 --> 00:04:25,852
can move the Buddha to bestow a miracle,

71
00:04:27,492 --> 00:04:28,532
I will pray as well,

72
00:04:28,532 --> 00:04:29,772
As long as it is real to people,

73
00:04:29,772 --> 00:04:31,172
