174
00:14:14,972 --> 00:14:16,492
So you wanted to kill her,

175
00:14:16,492 --> 00:14:18,452
My lady, it's absolutely a false accusation,

176
00:14:18,452 --> 00:14:20,492
If you don't believe me,
you could ask the coachman to come back,

177
00:14:20,492 --> 00:14:22,032
We can confront each other face to face,

178
00:14:22,032 --> 00:14:23,492
He has run away,

179
00:14:23,492 --> 00:14:25,412
Where can I go to find him?

180
00:14:25,412 --> 00:14:27,612
My lady, it wasn't me,

181
00:14:28,652 --> 00:14:29,732
It's not me,

182
00:16:20,172 --> 00:16:21,452
