185
00:16:29,172 --> 00:16:30,336
But let me make it clear in advance,

186
00:16:32,372 --> 00:16:34,252
if you ever think of hurting Liuli again,

187
00:16:35,012 --> 00:16:36,732
despite of giving up my official robe,

188
00:16:37,372 --> 00:16:39,412
