189
00:16:45,772 --> 00:16:46,848
Senior Official Pei,

190
00:16:48,012 --> 00:16:49,052
I am not responsible for this matter,

191
00:16:50,732 --> 00:16:51,932
If I wanted to kill you,

192
00:16:52,572 --> 00:16:54,412
you couldn't walk out of Dunhuang alive,

193
00:16:54,932 --> 00:16:55,968
Assassination

194
00:16:57,172 --> 00:16:58,252
is something I disdain,

195
00:16:59,252 --> 00:17:00,332
I hope so,

196
00:17:08,972 --> 00:17:10,812
I will ensure the safety of Madam Kudi

197
00:17:14,972 --> 00:17:16,612
for the honor of my Qu family,

198
00:17:23,772 --> 00:17:28,652
